{"tid":303070,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[RPi3] Backup問題","createTime":"2017-06-30T01:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T12:48:15.000Z","uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"204f9eb700dac9620c8fc51524fae72b8dd589fb","tid":303070,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n是Backup部RPi最正路方法咁當然係拎張SD卡出黎<br />\n之後整disk image啦<br />\n<br />\n但係RPi3個卡槽真係好撚實<br />\n次次都抆到手指痛(我有用殼所以冇位夾住張卡)<br />\n都唔知點解佢唔用彈弓卡槽<br />\n<br />\n咁所以我就想問吓有冇一啲方法唔拎張卡都整到disk image<br />\n除咗本身張卡唔會駁其他cloud/storage device<br />\n我亦唔想過程中有將disk image寫落張卡<br />\n初步構思係咁<br />\n<br />\n1. 整個volume snapshot<br />\n2. 將呢個volume snapshot指去某個path例如 ~/foo.img, 呢個file並唔係實際存在喺度, 只係模擬出黎<br />\n3. 咁我就可以經SFTP/SMB/webserver乜都好咁拎呢個disk image file走<br />\n<br />\n但係就未有頭緒要點做<br />\n其實咁樣可唔可行?<br />\n定係我只係天馬行空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147b0676e9d648f4c45ed70fa32cc4db29d0a2a6","tid":303070,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"backup data 定整個系統連 data backup ?"},{"pid":"78cd820db10d4a1a8f955431de764a474e84cfa3","tid":303070,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>backup data 定整個系統連 data backup ?</blockquote><br />\n後者<br />\n等同我拎張sd卡出嚟整disk image咁"},{"pid":"9926b78e312cdba8f0e3138322666e036cdc449c","tid":303070,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>backup data 定整個系統連 data backup ?</blockquote><br />\n後者<br />\n等同我拎張sd卡出嚟整disk image咁</blockquote><br />\n即係我要呢個image係可以用dd/win32diskimager寫返入sd卡"},{"pid":"eceb2c66b1b1dbafdad251c2de4e4f66ef408b37","tid":303070,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif